Disadvantages of Choreography Saga Pattern?
Рђб Workflow can become confusing when adding new steps, as it's difficult to track which saga participants listen to which commands.
Рђб There's a risk of cyclic dependency between saga participants because they have to consume each
other's commands
Рђб Integration testing is difficult because all services must be running to simulate a transaction.


What is Orchestration Saga Pattern?
Рђб Orchestration is a way to coordinate sagas where a centralized controller tells the saga participants what local transactions to execute.
Рђб The saga orchestrator handles all the transactions and tells the participants which operation to perform based on events.
Рђб The orchestrator
Рђб executes saga requests,
Рђб stores and interprets the states of each task,
Рђб handles failure recovery with compensating transactions.

