­ЪЉЅ JVM Architecture = Class Loader + Runtime Data Areas + Execution Engine.
* Class Loader Рєњ loads classes.
* Memory Areas Рєњ stores code, objects, variables.
* Execution Engine Рєњ runs bytecode (Interpreter + JIT + GC).



